attributes.title: Terrible app
attributes.review: I went to download this app and when It finally downloaded it was 2016 so I was very nervous on why it downloaded so late. So I open the app and my dog swallows my phone, I obviously panic and I reach my hand down his throat and pull out my cat. Being so modified I call my phone on my house phone, 20 mins later I give it and find out my phone was in my cats poop. I grab my phone and try to open the app again but my robber comes in and grabs my phone and throws it out the window. So I take his phone and download this app, rats come into my house. They all go inside his phone, so I call the police and when they answered they said to call back in 2021 when the year is over. So now I because of this dumb app, I have rats inside my house, my dog ate my cat again, my robber cheated on me with the girl next door, and my phone is flying in the clouds.
